your distance, but most of all,
in all that you do, make sure to

00:38:12.770 --> 00:38:22.170
do it in a way of your heritage,
the way of your culture, the
Samoan way, fa'asamoa. Thank

00:38:22.170 --> 00:38:23.370
you.


